{"id": "art-477", "label": "Art. 477", "title": "Art. 477: Conţinutul şi efectele hotărârii", "slug": "art-477", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 477: Con&#355;inutul &#351;i efectele hot&#259;rârii </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1240783666\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1374\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1240783666\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Asupra sesiz&#259;rii, completul pentru dezlegarea unor\nchestiuni de drept se pronun&#355;&#259; prin decizie, numai cu privire la\nchestiunea de drept supus&#259; dezleg&#259;rii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_129215721\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1373\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_129215721\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dispozi&#355;iile art. 474 alin. (3) se aplic&#259; în\nmod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_653373931\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1372\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_653373931\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Dezlegarea dat&#259; chestiunilor de drept este\nobligatorie pentru instan&#355;e de la data public&#259;rii deciziei în\nMonitorul Oficial al României, Partea I.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_208489434\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1371\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_208489434\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)[textul din Art. 477, alin. (4) din partea 2, titlul\nIII, capitolul VI, sectiunea 2 a fost abrogat la 23-mai-2016 de </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>Art. II, punctul 117. din Ordonanta urgenta 18/2016</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>]</span></p>"}